::GoldenEye::
She set down next to Dollen and looked around. "Seams we have missed 
the fight." she said as she layed eyes on the burn marks on the 
ground and saw what looked like scrap metal from a bot.  She moved 
closer to Dollen. "Well, we're here, where are they?"

::KitKat::
She head the message and replied. "We are now in the Destron's old 
base.  I'll send you the co-ordinants."  She transmitted the 
loccation of the base to Dollen.
